<codeline><highlight class="normal">```python</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>transport/quic.py:686</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>当前:<sp/>每次完整握手</highlight></codeline>
