<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>当前:<sp/>同步锁竞争</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">async<sp/>def<sp/>open_stream(self)<sp/>-&gt;<sp/>YamuxStream:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>async<sp/>with<sp/>self._stream_id_lock:<sp/><sp/>#<sp/>瓶颈:<sp/>全局锁</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>stream_id<sp/>=<sp/>self._next_stream_id</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>self._next_stream_id<sp/>+=<sp/>STREAM_ID_INCREMENT</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>async<sp/>with<sp/>self._streams_lock:<sp/><sp/>#<sp/>瓶颈:<sp/>第二次锁</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>if<sp/>stream_id<sp/>in<sp/>self._streams:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>raise<sp/>YamuxProtocolError(...)</highlight></codeline>
