<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>2.1<sp/>TCP<sp/>传输优化</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">####<sp/>TCP<sp/>Fast<sp/>Open<sp/>(TFO)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```python</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>新增:<sp/>transport/tcp_tfo.py</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">class<sp/>TCPFastOpenTransport:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>&quot;&quot;&quot;支持<sp/>TCP<sp/>Fast<sp/>Open<sp/>的<sp/>TCP<sp/>传输&quot;&quot;&quot;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>async<sp/>def<sp/>dial(self,<sp/>addr:<sp/>str)<sp/>-&gt;<sp/>Connection:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#<sp/>使用<sp/>MSG_FASTOPEN<sp/>或<sp/>socket.connect()<sp/>+<sp/>TFO</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#<sp/>目标:<sp/>将连接延迟从<sp/>~50ms<sp/>降至<sp/>&lt;20ms</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
