<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>第二次连接:<sp/>接近<sp/>0ms<sp/>(使用<sp/>TFO<sp/>cookie)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>2.2<sp/>Yamux<sp/>优化</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">####<sp/>流<sp/>ID<sp/>预分配池</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```python</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>优化:<sp/>muxer/yamux_optimized.py</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">class<sp/>YamuxSessionOptimized:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>def<sp/>__init__(self,<sp/>...):</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#<sp/>预分配<sp/>64<sp/>个流<sp/>ID</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>self._stream_id_pool<sp/>=<sp/>Queue(maxsize=64)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>for<sp/>i<sp/>in<sp/>range(64):</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>self._stream_id_pool.put_nowait(self._next_stream_id<sp/>+<sp/>i<sp/>*<sp/>2)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>self._next_stream_id<sp/>+=<sp/>128</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>async<sp/>def<sp/>open_stream(self)<sp/>-&gt;<sp/>YamuxStream:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#<sp/>无锁获取预分配<sp/>ID</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>stream_id<sp/>=<sp/>await<sp/>self._stream_id_pool.get()</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>...</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">预期收益：</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>流创建延迟:<sp/>5ms<sp/>→<sp/>&lt;2ms<sp/>(60%<sp/>改善)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">-<sp/>并发流创建:<sp/>无锁竞争</highlight></codeline>
